### Docker instructions

#### Quick build and run
```
docker build -t carmelo0x63/resuman:<tag> --load .

docker run --rm carmelo0x63/resuman:<tag>
```

#### Build multiplatform image
```
docker buildx build --no-cache --platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64,linux/arm/v7 -t carmelo0x63/resuman:<tag> --load .
```

